{
  "stem": "1511.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And God helped that one day, we were packed in the wagons, and we couldn't take anything with, whatever you had-- money or something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or this ring was a heavy ring, which we had got married, and my husband had one like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when I came to Canada, I made up this ring, a signet, you call it, something like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my daughter have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She wants to have it for memory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My husband, his, also-- so we made-- bought other rings, and we made it like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my other daughter keeps it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She wants to have a souvenir from that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they put us in the trains, and that we're going back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was-- still the war was going on, but they were pushing back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was in 1946, starting with.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we came under-- they put us in the trains with food-- with no food, and we were starting to come closer to Bratslav, where we were going.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was [NON-ENGLISH], they called-- these people from the partisan but Goyim-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they came from all the sides from the bushes, and they took the driver.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They told the driver to stop the train, and we had a lot of Lubavitch people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were coming with us, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They also wanted to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they went from train to train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They started from the back, and whatever you have, and then they start killing the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So whatever you had, and they had-- give it to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so my husband and another few guys, whoever was-- they organized right away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The wives and the kids off the train, off the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in the bushes, we went in the corn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was at night, in the middle of the night, whoever could.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
